{"tid":1246652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際]歐洲拎忍唔住介入講幾句","createTime":"2019-06-20T22:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T23:58:20.000Z","uid":264032,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9edb36da7de402e80e309dd5ad2ff2c921266786","tid":1246652,"uid":264032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T22:25:49.000Z","msg":"親愛嘅香港朋友：<br />\n<br />\n自問離開咗香港一排，好少睇香港發生咩事。<br />\n但係過去呢兩星期我喺呢度日日追POST，晚晚都好擔心六一二會重演。<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔太方便講立場，不過我喺歐洲呢面已經做得幾多就幾多。<br />\n想同你哋講嘅係，愛沙尼亞已經有幾篇輿論有講香港。<br />\n有哥倫比亞嘅記者朋友更加幫小弟有關香港自治嘅文章譯做西班牙文上報。<br />\n<br />\n無論大家對六二一嘅取向係咩都好，記住要堅守自己嘅原則。<br />\n香港人，全世界係睇緊你吔嘅！<br />\n<br />\n追夢人上 <br />\n<br />\n&quot;To the first man who sacrificed himself for Hong Kong&quot; （致：為香港犠牲嘅第一個男人）<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.ut.ee/to-the-first-man-who-sacrificed-himself-for-hong-kong/?fbclid=IwAR0-A7SRInWYOwk1BO_hbNX-JzaCnN7QbSN4x-yxXBq_AlzF1bP_TPvMtiQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.ut.ee%2Fto-the-first-man-who-sacrificed-himself-for-hong-kong%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0-A7SRInWYOwk1BO_hbNX-JzaCnN7QbSN4x-yxXBq_AlzF1bP_TPvMtiQ&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=a6186ebc\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.ut.ee/to-the-first-man-who-sacrificed-himself-for-hong-kong/?fbclid=IwAR0-A7SRInWYOwk1BO_hbNX-JzaCnN7QbSN4x-yxXBq_AlzF1bP_TPvMtiQ</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;On amending Hong Kong&rsquo;s extradition legislation&quot; （有關香港嘅引渡條例修正案）<br />\n<a href=\"http://auke.ee/blog/iverson-ng-on-amending-hong-kongs-extradition-legislation/?fbclid=IwAR3_X0CDtrY0qbldXILFp0tG4XuvHKLq4IhanTstgoijjKwSKM7yD5bomUI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fauke.ee%2Fblog%2Fiverson-ng-on-amending-hong-kongs-extradition-legislation%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3_X0CDtrY0qbldXILFp0tG4XuvHKLq4IhanTstgoijjKwSKM7yD5bomUI&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=9dae8b8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://auke.ee/blog/iverson-ng-on-amending-hong-kongs-extradition-legislation/?fbclid=IwAR3_X0CDtrY0qbldXILFp0tG4XuvHKLq4IhanTstgoijjKwSKM7yD5bomUI</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Hongkonglane Eestis: toetage teise v&auml;ikeriigi v&otilde;itlusi, sest te teate, mis tunne oli olla &uuml;ksi suurv&otilde;imude vahel&quot;(港人在愛沙尼亞：小國需要幫助，因為愛沙尼亞好清楚被大國夾住係咩情況）<br />\n<a href=\"https://epl.delfi.ee/arvamus/hongkonglane-eestis-toetage-teise-vaikeriigi-voitlusi-sest-te-teate-mis-tunne-oli-olla-uksi-suurvoimude-vahel?id=86594317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepl.delfi.ee%2Farvamus%2Fhongkonglane-eestis-toetage-teise-vaikeriigi-voitlusi-sest-te-teate-mis-tunne-oli-olla-uksi-suurvoimude-vahel%3Fid%3D86594317&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=05a8bc4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://epl.delfi.ee/arvamus/hongkonglane-eestis-toetage-teise-vaikeriigi-voitlusi-sest-te-teate-mis-tunne-oli-olla-uksi-suurvoimude-vahel?id=86594317</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Hongkonglane Delfile: noortel protestijatel pole enam midagi kaotada&quot;（港人同DELFIE講：後生示威者已經無嘢好輸）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.delfi.ee/news/paevauudised/valismaa/intervjuu-hongkonglane-delfile-noortel-protestijatel-pole-enam-midagi-kaotada?id=86530417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.delfi.ee%2Fnews%2Fpaevauudised%2Fvalismaa%2Fintervjuu-hongkonglane-delfile-noortel-protestijatel-pole-enam-midagi-kaotada%3Fid%3D86530417&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=aa40199e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.delfi.ee/news/paevauudised/valismaa/intervjuu-hongkonglane-delfile-noortel-protestijatel-pole-enam-midagi-kaotada?id=86530417</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Hong Kong y su lucha por la autonom&iacute;a&quot;（香港為自治而爭扎）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elnuevosiglo.com.co/articulos/06-2019-hong-kong-y-su-lucha-por-la-autonomia?fbclid=IwAR0au-Cahh4-XXIFjfGSvASCuILBwOtWGXTFbt_ZQYLF_32-m_3sGNz0HnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elnuevosiglo.com.co%2Farticulos%2F06-2019-hong-kong-y-su-lucha-por-la-autonomia%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0au-Cahh4-XXIFjfGSvASCuILBwOtWGX